      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes and discusses the issues involved in the design of the modern accounting systems.  The field of Accounting Management is concerned with the collection the collection of resource consumption data for the purposes of capacity and trend analysis, cost allocation, auditing, and billing.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
